quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,72,"Mi ten$am yiwen, wa irra p id $ef wa. Öebbi Issuffe$ ed ayen teppeffrem"
  2,73,"Nenna: \"ewwtet ep s kra ines\". Akka i Issidir Öebbi lmeggtin. Issenâat awen issekniyen iS, amar a pfehmem"
  2,74,"Sinna, deffir waya, qquôen wulawen nnwen; cuban aéôu, ne$ kteô, di ta$eôt. Ih, llan iéôa iseg d pfeggiven isaffen. Llan, s tidep, wid ipceqqiqen, teff$en d waman segsen. S tidep, llan wid i$ellin si tugwdi n Öebbi. Ur I$fil Öebbi $ef wayen txeddmem"
  2,75,"Day tôe$bem a kwen amnen? Ni$ arbaâ, segsen, ssemêasen i wawal n Öebbi, sinna, mi t fehmen, ad as bedlen udem, u nitni éôan"
  2,76,"Mi mmugren wid iumnen, ad inin: \"numen\". Mi qqimen garasen, qqaôen: \"day ad asen tinim ayen i wen Imla Öebbi, a kwen nna$en yis, ar Mass nnwen? Day ur tepmeyyizem ara"
  2,77,"Ne$ ur éôin ara, Öebbi Issen ayen teffren, akked wayen qqaôen"
  2,78,"Garasen, at war ta$uôi, ur nessin Tazmamt, siwa ayen nnwan. Nitni $ilen kan"
  2,79,"A tawa$it n wid ipparun Tazmamt s ifassen nnsen, sinna, qqaôen: \"ayagi s$uô Öebbi\", iwakken ad a$en, yis, ayen ôxisen! A tawa$it nnsen, ilmend n wayen uran ifassen nnsen! A tawa$it nnsen, $ef wayen keppben"
  2,80,"Nnan: \"ur a$ tepnal tmes, d awez$i, siwa kra n wussan\". Ini: \"day teîîfem lemâahda s$uô Öebbi? Öebbi, d awez$i, ur Izeggil lemâahda S. Ne$ teqqaôem, $ef Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem"
  2,81,"Xaîi, win ikesben tucmip, u tennev as tuccva s…, widak, d at tmes, degs ad wekkôen"
  2,82,"Wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, widak, d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen"